<br>
The Marine Corps isnt for everyone. Mission always comes first. So when they recieve money for a base they buildthe required facilities first and build the recreation stuff with whats left.<br>
<br>
If Your Brother has the scores, go airforce if you arent staying in for a career. More oportunity for schooling and education training while in. If he wants a career investigate all 4 services and pick the one that fits his image of what he wants to be.<br>
<br>
Pride in self and service is rather important, something some of the services have forgotten and dont teach their people.<br>
<br>
